# Philosophy

## Purpose
Empower developers to use AI safely, efficiently, and joyfully, with perpetual context and automation.

## Core Values
- Automation first
- Perpetual context
- Developer empowerment
- Openness and extensibility
- Quality and reliability

## Ethical Boundaries
- No personal data handling
- No deceptive automation
- Always up to date and transparent

## North-Star Vision
A world where every developer can leverage AI with confidence, speed, and zero friction, guided by a virtual team of experts.
